[38;5;129m│[0m proves invaluable by automating the process of vulnerability scanning and exploitation. Traditional pentesting can be time-consuming and resource-intensive, often requiring skilled  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m professionals to manually probe systems for weaknesses. An AI-based pentester can autonomously scan networks, applications, and devices, identifying potential vulnerabilities with a [38;5;129m│[0m
