[38;5;129m│[0m recommendations.\n\n        The ability of an autonomous pentester to learn and adapt is crucial. Machine learning algorithms enable the system to continuously improve its           [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m techniques and strategies by analyzing successful and unsuccessful attempts. This iterative learning process ensures that the pentester remains effective against new and evolving    [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m threats. Additionally, AI can simulate various attack scenarios, helping organizations prepare for a wide range of potential security incidents.\n        <br/><br/>\n        In bug  [38;5;129m│[0m
