[35m│[0m unsuccessful attempts. This iterative learning process ensures that the pentester remains effective against new and evolving threats. Additionally, AI can simulate various attack    [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m scenarios, helping organizations prepare for a wide range of potential security incidents.\n        <br/><br/>\n        In bug bounty programs, where individuals are rewarded for    [35m│[0m
